# Simplified List UI Patterns

## Overview
This rule defines the simplified UI patterns for Customers and Account Managers pages without accordion systems or KPI cards.

## UI Structure Pattern

### 1. Page Header Structure
Simple header without KPI cards:

```typescript
<div className="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border">
  <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
    <h3 className="text-lg font-semibold">Customers</h3>
    {selectedCustomer && (
      <Button variant="outline" onClick={() => setSelectedCustomer(null)}>
        Back to All Customers
      </Button>
    )}
  </div>
</div>
```

### 2. List Item Structure
Clean, simple cards without accordion functionality:

```typescript
<div className="space-y-2">
  {customers.map((customer) => (
    <div key={customer.id} className="border rounded-lg bg-card p-4">
      <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div className="flex items-center space-x-3">
          <h4 className="font-semibold">{customer.name}</h4>
          <span className="text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            ({customer.games.length} games, {customer.totalInstalls.toLocaleString()} installs)
          </span>
        </div>
        <Button
          variant="default"
          size="default"
          onClick={() => setSelectedCustomer(customer.id)}
          className="font-semibold"
        >
          View Files
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  ))}
</div>
```

## Button Styling Standards

### Primary Action Button
Use consistent styling for main action buttons:

```typescript
<Button
  variant="default"        // Blue background
  size="default"          // Standard size
  className="font-semibold" // Bold text for emphasis
  onClick={handleAction}
>
  View Files
</Button>
```

### Secondary Action Button
Use outline variant for secondary actions:

```typescript
<Button 
  variant="outline" 
  onClick={handleBackAction}
>
  Back to All Customers
</Button>
```

## Layout Standards

### Card Spacing
- Use `space-y-2` for vertical spacing between cards
- Use `p-4` for card padding
- Use `border rounded-lg bg-card` for card styling

### Content Alignment
- Use `flex items-center justify-between` for horizontal layout
- Use `space-x-3` for spacing between elements
- Use `text-sm text-muted-foreground` for secondary information

## Information Display Pattern

### Primary Information
- Customer/Manager name: `font-semibold`
- Always display in the main text area

### Secondary Information
- Games count, installs count: `text-sm text-muted-foreground`
- Display in parentheses format: `(2 games, 45.716 installs)`

## Critical Rules
- ✅ No accordion functionality - simple cards only
- ✅ No KPI cards in page headers
- ✅ Consistent button styling with `variant="default"` and `font-semibold`
- ✅ Clean spacing with `space-y-2` and `p-4`
- ✅ Secondary information in muted text
- ✅ Horizontal layout with `flex items-center justify-between`
- ✅ Remove all ChevronDown/ChevronRight icons
- ✅ Remove all accordion state management